{"tid":1857890,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想整啲對香港人有用既資源：武漢肺炎來襲會重現SARS慘況?!大家準備左幾多積蓄做防守?","createTime":"2020-02-02T11:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T05:56:28.000Z","uid":343020,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"68580940108f68cb8beedc32cc5c7d1a07b156e9","tid":1857890,"uid":343020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:29:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>武漢肺炎來襲會重現SARS慘況?!打工仔需知的3個應變方案(個人理財篇)!你的防守力夠嗎?政府/學校不會告訴你的經濟真相</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BCCpf4xFzjk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBCCpf4xFzjk&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9FgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=4b3ed245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BCCpf4xFzjk</a><br />\n<br />\n應變方案1:增加收入來源(freelance,兼職,slash)<br />\n應變方案2:減少開支(分清必要/想要)<br />\n應變方案3:避免負債<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n自問唔係專家，只係一些透過個人經驗不斷學習翻黎的心得和分享<br />\n<br />\n我既目標係希望盡量幫香港人可以搜集一些免費實用/含經濟效益/搵到食既資料<br />\n<br />\n計劃黎緊主要會上載既片/資源題材包括<br />\n求職/轉工<br />\n職業發展<br />\n進修〔搵下有冇啲可以幫大家有一技之長/移民(唔係冇選擇都唔鼓勵)加分既知識〕<br />\n其他實用野等等...稔到再整<br />\n<br />\n大家如果係搵工／進修上面有咩疑難都可以盡量係到問，我答到盡力答"},{"pid":"06c8923ff01fa6ffce33bd94cf54ed4c67eade87","tid":1857890,"uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:31:24.000Z","msg":"1:增加收入來源<br />\n<br />\n炒口罩？"},{"pid":"9b20b86320ae6c1a97661e1e00e52ecf22be0c9d","tid":1857890,"uid":249475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06c8923ff01fa6ffce33bd94cf54ed4c67eade87","tid":1857890,"uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:31:24.000Z","msg":"1:增加收入來源<br />\n<br />\n炒口罩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"生產口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3599c764d19f9c3871c1b7602e633627e0e33bc","tid":1857890,"uid":249475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img s